0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:03:50.000Z","msg":"佢地有冇犯到郊野公園條例任何一條？<br />\n我覺得可以組織驅蝗行動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"好似要指定地方同有限幾多個營"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:11:04.000Z","msg":"係時候要搞，咁樣落去d垃圾積到上天<br />\n因為俾左錢就以為老奉唔駛處理"},{"pid":"d192b173521c6dd3a8881fe3cb43cbe5fefe512d","tid":648681,"uid":67657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"尋日搭車經過筲箕灣巴士總站<br />\n見到去石澳架巴士坐滿哂人,等車條人龍依然多到要排上天橋,9成都係蝗蟲<br />\n石澳rip"},{"pid":"8a7b51a76d61c1d5a735a6974fd9cb20aa45686d","tid":648681,"uid":29090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"其實係咪可以整個禁區？<br />\n屌那星度度都係支那蟲真係眼冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cc1f81ba719fcd732d86d3e5087ed2b8f60b8e","tid":648681,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"第二張條女好似ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab06d8ea8c9b442559d37b3e4c3be0c563eae25","tid":648681,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"43cc1f81ba719fcd732d86d3e5087ed2b8f60b8e","tid":648681,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"第二張條女好似ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:38:18.000Z","msg":"五毛點扮香港人<br />\n都好容易篤穿<br />\n<br />\n因為根本唔同地方文化既人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癡綫佬</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n. 駡人神經病的廣東話是: &quot;黐線&quot;, 好像腦子的線路黏在一塊, 人就儍了. <br />\n香港人現在常寫成&quot;癡線&quot;或&quot;痴線&quot;, 可能是筆劃較少之故. 其實癡和痴是&quot;迷戀&quot; 的意思, 最多是寫成為&quot;痴呆&quot;, 雖然都和精神問題有點關連, 但難以和&quot;線&quot;扯上關係. <br />\n2. 据字典上说，&quot;痴'和&quot;癡&quot;兩個字沒有分別, 可以寫&ldquo;痴呆&rdquo;或 &ldquo;癡呆&rdquo;。国内简化汉字统一为&ldquo;痴&rdquo; <br />\n3. 線和綫兩個字也是一樣的, 前者是正寫, 後者是俗寫, 大部份情況寫任何一個都可以, 只是有些情況向來用其中一個, 應該跟從, 如: 無綫電視 <br />\n国内简化汉字统一为&ldquo;线&rdquo; <br />\n4. 綫字打不出只是和字庫舊 / 收字少有關. 在較新的字庫, 打&quot;女火戈戈&quot;就可以 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2007-06-26 18:18:54 補充： <br />\n癡線 / 黐線 / 痴綫只是粵語口語, 不宜作書寫用, 要寫的話, 還是寫普通話書面語的 - 瘋了 / 神經病等等比較好"},{"pid":"64ced7c519dfd761dcfa3e3a7c0976699e8c1c7c","tid":648681,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"啲環保撚同機構又失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cde30249b77c7ef029bb90e52bb22d073d8331d","tid":648681,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"一日唔燒到埋班師奶到 你都未洗旨意話中國唔好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfc8e968d17026a2b718173d72c7e0d4bd23bb0","tid":648681,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:45:22.000Z","msg":"災難"},{"pid":"2bb97f57670c08faa4ba65694498c6d1f0644563","tid":648681,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"唔怪得嗰陣架仔要限支拿人與狗不得進入"},{"pid":"646248265aea3bb59bb02fdedd9a3c1d3267e0c9","tid":648681,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"燒左個西貢咪可以去起樓羅"},{"pid":"3b757872a52dd84be598f6cadd27224c5a23f9b9","tid":648681,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"Cut佢老味水，等班仆街大熱天時變鹹魚"},{"pid":"e90be72a46e3eef60a95eafe8739c490f7c06c3d","tid":648681,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"220768493b2199260f4b322eb213e87d555a605d","tid":648681,"uid":12449,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"r